<p><b>Breviary application | What\'s new</b>

<p><b>Version 1.12:</b>
<ul>
<li> Possibility to display communia.
<li> Corrections for all languages.
<li> Typos and fixes for all languages.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.11.2:</b>
<ul>
<li> New menu item: Display only normal font (vs use also bold font).
<li> Typos and fixes for all languages.
<li> Added new settings.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.11.1:</b>
<ul>
<li> Liturgical readings: Backward compatibility with Android 2.x and older.
<li> Typos and fixes for all languages.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.11:</b>
<ul>
<li> Switching night/day mode from main menu.
<li> Bigger line height for better readability.
<li> Updated “About” dialog.
<li> Many typos for all languages.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.10.1:</b>
<ul>
<li> Minor fixes.
<li> Many typos for all languages.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.10:</b>
<ul>
<li> Setting for displaying text of prayer in blind-friendly mode (only prayer text, without headings & rubrics) suitable for text-to-speech output.
<li> New option in main screen: Ordinarium.
<li> Fix of night-mode for Mary antiphones (compline).
<li> Compatibility with Android 5.0 Lollipop.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.9.10:</b>
<ul>
<li> Setting for automatic turning on silent mode when praying.
<li> SK + HU: New option for first vespers hymn (ordinary time).
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.9.9:</b>
<ul>
<li> SK: CSS formatting of hymns.
<li> HU: Plenty of small fixes & CSS formatting.
</ul>

<p><b>Version 1.9.8:</b>
<ul>
<li> Long tap hides bottom navigation bar.
<li> Added option for not-dimming screen.
<li> SK: Various fixes.
<li> CZ: CSS formatting of psalms and canticles.
<li> HU: Plenty of small fixes.
</ul>

</body></html>
